### COMPILE ERROR FIX REFERENCE (apply the matching fix for each error above):

**"xxx 在 ClassName 中是 private 访问控制" (private field/method access)**
→ NEVER access private fields/methods directly. Use reflection:
```java
Field f = ClassName.class.getDeclaredField("fieldName");
f.setAccessible(true);
Object val = f.get(instance);
// For private method:
Method m = ClassName.class.getDeclaredMethod("methodName", ArgType.class);
m.setAccessible(true);
m.invoke(instance, args);
```

**"无法从最终ClassName进行继承" (cannot extend final class)**
→ Remove anonymous subclass. Use Mockito spy:
```java
ClassName spy = Mockito.spy(new ClassName(args));
doThrow(new IOException()).when(spy).someMethod();
```

**"不兼容的类型: Closeable/Flushable无法转换为Appendable"**
→ Replace Closeable/Flushable mock with a type that implements Appendable:
```java
