**"对于assertThrows(Class,...,(e)->...)" (wrong lambda parameter)**
→ Use zero-argument lambda for assertThrows:
```java
assertThrows(IOException.class, () -> obj.method());  // NO parameter in lambda
// NOT: assertThrows(IOException.class, e -> obj.method());
```

